WEBVTT

00:04:26.203 --> 00:04:30.865
like this sign on the side
of the highway in Texas.

00:04:30.889 --> 00:04:32.039
[TEMPTATIONS]

00:04:32.063 --> 00:04:34.689
They can often signify things
that we can't see at all,

00:04:34.713 --> 00:04:36.752
like the distance to our destination.

00:04:36.776 --> 00:04:40.014
Signs often help to orient us in the world

00:04:40.038 --> 00:04:41.189
[You are on an island]

00:04:41.213 --> 00:04:42.752
by telling us where we are now

00:04:42.776 --> 00:04:44.990
and what's happening
in the present moment,

00:04:45.014 --> 00:04:47.680
but they can also help us zoom out,

00:04:47.704 --> 00:04:49.720
shift our perspective

00:04:49.744 --> 00:04:52.411
and get a glimpse of the bigger picture.

00:04:53.014 --> 00:04:55.736
Imagine, for example,

00:04:55.760 --> 00:04:58.691
you're walking down
the street in Philadelphia.

00:04:59.081 --> 00:05:02.731
A city in the US that contains
so much history,